rows.label: qst701504_msg0002
rows.name:
How very odd. The inn's open but no
one's around.

rows.label: qst701504_msg0003
rows.name: I hope nothing's happened to him...

rows.label: qst701504_msg0004
rows.name:
Wait here, miss.
We'll have a look around.

rows.label: qst701504_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm not sure if it means anything, but
I spotted some footprints out front.
Maybe they lead somewhere?

rows.label: qst701504_msg0006
rows.name:
You've got a sharp pair of eyes there,
missus!

rows.label: qst701504_msg0007
rows.name:
Heh heh. I was just so nervous about
seeing my husband again that I had
my eyes fixed on the ground...

rows.label: qst701504_msg0008
rows.name:
I just don't know how I'll feel when I
see him, or how I should behave...

rows.label: qst701504_msg0009
rows.name:
It feels like being a young woman again!
Even though I know we can't turn back
time...
